{
  "texts": [
    "Variants of different constituents within sentences were separately analyzed, including subject (shown in Fig. 10b), object (shown in Fig.",
    "10c), and predicate (shown in Fig. 10d).",
    "To examine the temporal changes of variant usage, we utilized diachronic n-gram functionality to assess the frequency changes of the top five most frequently used variants.",
    "The timeline spans from the Spring and Autumn periods to the Northern and Southern Dynasties periods (excluding the brief Qin dynasty), and our built-in corpus nearly comprehensively encompasses literary works created during this interval.",
    "The results are displayed in Fig. 10e."
  ]
}